## Purpose of This Portfolio

This portfolio demonstrates how executive leadership, business strategy, and emerging technologies—AI, machine learning, cloud computing, and digital transformation—come together to solve real organizational problems.

Each project is structured as an executive case study, showing:
- The business problem
- The technical approach
- The results
- The business impact

